name: Meltryllis (Fate) Lora
description: This is Meltryllis (fate), first file is trained with DDosMixv2, 2nd updated file uses AbyssOrangeMix2 - Hardcore, can make SFW, and NSFW, mostly trained with her in her famous swimsuit. file 1was trained with 330 images, and UPDATE file uses 840 images of anime and real life. best weight is to use for first file is 0.6, UPDATE file weight 1 works best. I would love for you all to show your renders in the comments. if yall want me to make a model for you just comment and ill work on one.

modelVersions.name: MeltryllisV2+realism
modelVersions.description:
this is MeltryllisV2 the way better an improved version of MeltryllisV1.

now you can make Semi-realistic renders, to real-life renders. if you want to make your character look like a cosplayer use a realistic CKPT like DdosMix and SunshineMix. the best weight to use for the prompt is (0.8-1). using 1 I've gotten the best results. trained using AbyssOrangeMix2 - Hardcore for a softer realistic anime look. this can do SFW and NSFW. if you don't type anything in the prompt nsfw wise you don't have to worry. This took 17hrs total to train using 840 images of anime and real life. please I would love it if you would share your renders in the comments. links will be at the bottom

https://civitai.com/models/4451/abyssorangemix2-hardcore

https://civitai.com/models/8437/ddosmix
